## TennUs Privacy Policy

Welcome to TennUs for wearable!

This is a free to use app made by myself in my free time. 
I have not programmed this app to collect any personally identifiable information. All data is created by the you (the user) is stored on your device only, this includes your tennis score and match preferences.This can be simply erased by clearing the app's data or uninstalling it.

If you find any security vulnerability that has been inadvertently caused by me, or have any question regarding how the app protectes your privacy, please send me an email and I will surely try to fix it/help you.

I hold no liability against any and all damages.

Yours sincerely,
Joshua,
Ireland
